reviewText:
This was a great DVD that had a mix of episodes from two different seasons. The episodes were fun and I really liked the messages of friendship, teamwork and more that were shown in these episodes. While this is not a full season, the mix of episodes was good and definitely worked! All-in-all this was a great DVD with fun episodes that will keep bringing you back for more!

*I received this for review - all opinions are my own*

Google never fails me when it comes to finding out about the episodes for LPS dvds and here is the latest batch:
1. So interesting (season 2)
2. What's so scary about the jungle? Everything! (Season 3)
3. Feud for thought (Season 3)
4. Fish out of water (Season 3)
5. Proud as a... peacock? (Season 3)
